description:
Today we tackle one of the most powerful advice calls we've ever received (53:30) but first, Anna and Sim sit down with the hilarious Jim Jefferies (THE JIM JEFFERIES SHOW, LEGIT) and discuss his best friend Brad Pitt (5:30), the top three things Jim misses about Australia (8:30), and burritos (15:00). Next they play a new game called “Pick Your Fate” (17:00) and then some wild deal-breakers (31:00).

Later, they call at Miranda (53:30) which you DO NOT want to skip. Tune in!
